            "reviewer_title": "Shooting Sport Enthusiaist",
            "review_text": "I've been using the GRWOLF FlexTarget Smart GBB Replica Training Target for a few weeks now for indoor airsoft training, and it's honestly one of the best investments I've made for improving my skills without needing to head to an outdoor range every time. This smart electronic target turns solo practice into something genuinely engaging and data-driven—perfect for apartment, basement, or garage setups where space and noise are concerns.\n\nWhat It Actually Is\nIt's a compact, shot-proof interactive target (medium size, about 8 kg / 17.6 lbs) designed specifically for airsoft GBB (Gas Blow Back) replicas, but it also works great for other low-velocity training. The big selling point is the app-connected smart system: it detects hits via built-in sensors, lights up or reacts visually, tracks your performance in real time, and feeds everything into a phone app for custom drills, scoring, and progress history.",
            "review_date": "05/01/2026"
          }
        },
