            "review_text": "A Game Changer for Serious Training!\n\nMy son shoots 2,000 rounds every single day, and this target has been an absolute lifesaver. We used to go through mountains of paper targets and spend a fortune constantly replacing those sticky target sheets. Not anymore — this thing just keeps going. The time and money we've saved is unreal. Honestly, at this point we couldn't train without it. If your kid is putting in serious volume like mine, stop wasting money on disposables and just get one of these. Absolutely love it!",
